Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====AVANT=====
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月31日下午3点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名5岁男童不慎从清水区一栋公营住房的阳台跌落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼看就要受重伤时被一名路人接住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男童受轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了他的路人是一名女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她没有留下姓名就离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她背着个乐器箱  看起来行色匆匆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谁  这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是穗村千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是市民文化会馆的大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是要说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是吹奏乐大赛地区选拔赛的当日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那立下大功的女高中生的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕扭了  腰差点断了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家后昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要在这里演奏
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====A  PART=====
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明离开幕式还有很久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平时的自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越临近上场就越紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我在你手心写个『人』字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  请不要抛弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}喂  住手  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃排球后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有长笛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}别人会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是要倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要坚持到表演完成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能继续坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.68,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&Hdad9d9&\fs21\an7\bord0.7}静冈县中部地区\N\N{\fs26}吹奏乐大赛\N\N{\fs19}高中B部门\N{\fs16}8月1日  上午10点开始\N{\fs16}静冈市民文化会馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接住5岁的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该受了很大冲击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在赛前受伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能吹长笛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有告诉大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能一大早就动摇他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在会场动摇就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们  不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹泽  你了解情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚她们母女哭着来求我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直子也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么叫她直子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是青梅竹马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么伤势如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点肿  但似乎没大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于演奏  深夜在河边检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她又犯了和前一天相同的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真结实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一天？为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆撞到脑袋变成天才长笛少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个女生深夜在河边练习没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上条君也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说我更担心他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他听说了之后幸灾乐祸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}我等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果穗村同学和他打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被猫抓的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一只可爱的猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只仅有精力充沛这一优点的坏猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上条君  你到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我碰上一个迷路的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上条前辈好从容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是地区比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来采访的记者也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  为了不引起麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要像忍者一样偷偷藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目标应该不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股怪味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太你洗澡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一股野兽的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人住很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该在外面的河边洗下澡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  草壁老师还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说好了在会场会合…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我们的出场顺序在26个学校中排在倒数第二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2点携乐器进入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2点30分调整乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2点50分在舞台后方待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3点出场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼花缭乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然乐器2点才到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么早进会场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分部员都是首次参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟悉下会场比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  你们在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堺老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在A部门地区选拔赛中轻松突围了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目标是在全国大赛上来一次最棒的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤咲高中今天B部门也会出赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我想当藤咲高中的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大猩猩就是你的顾问了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是穗村和上条？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和传闻一样的组合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  我来转达草壁老师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁老师的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让堺老师你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我联系了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问他需不需要我们借的练习场地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我们出场顺序靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午场地都空着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁老师说他会比预定晚1小时进场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约会在1点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  由部长下达指示  领导部员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  如果有人来采访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开头集中的地方非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铜管乐器的合奏也出色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我听说他们去年只得了铜奖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才铜奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能比铜奖差对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是清水南高中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有吹奏乐部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好没面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了不被气氛吞没才提早进来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出自信  取得胜利通往县大赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想在这里结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说上条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上开始他的行动就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后藤同学  看好我的包和长笛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会真的在这洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里能带宠物来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由作家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我采访下你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要让我露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想报道英勇救人的女高中生的事迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于东海地区比赛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是初次参加B部门的无名校…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们清水南高中会顺利进入县大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B部门的参赛学校有26所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年获得金奖的10所学校全部进入了县大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场大赛没有得了金奖却不参加下一轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然确实获得了金奖就能进入下一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道我们能不能获得金奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对自己的评价太低了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过你们的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过在清水的联合练习录像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能把无名吹奏部培养成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是那个草壁真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道草壁老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5年前  他被称为古典音乐界的宠儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上每年都人才辈出  但他在其中亦别具一格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃耀眼的生涯  神秘失踪的草壁真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为无名吹奏部的顾问  努力再次登上舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人会对此不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能直接问他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会跟着你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  因为藤咲高中那个什么堺老师的干预
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会场内的学生都不和我们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能不管这事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为草壁真一郎丢下你们不去会场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明身为你们的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我走开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  不许直呼老师的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才在对单纯的千夏大言不惭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丛林大帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那个阻塞音非常厉害的长号手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要动摇我们的部员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快上台表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个叫堺的老师的安排下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计下午的采访限制会很严格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想趁现在把话问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要做个交易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今早在这发现的一条迷路的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮忙找一下它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全足以提供你的新闻材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只狗有那么厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,628)\an5}チベタン·マスティフ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏獒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(617,628)\an5}ちべたん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏…猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25}注：たん是日语里的爱称之一，这里千夏不认识藏獒以为是狗的名字加爱称
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏獒  在日本还不太知名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种生息在青藏高原的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与牧羊犬并称世界两大军用犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是纯种的  价值数百万至数千万日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只狗这么贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要永远和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下雪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天使来迎接你之前和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它要和我一起生活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不定一生都会孑然一身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才让它养我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是金钱的奴隶  请不要管他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这只很贵的狗先寄放在你那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你找到它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  主人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只…是我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出现了一位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人有两位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们捡到狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得谁是真正的主人  就还给谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的  就让我在这里旁观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代版的所罗门断案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这样的材料啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====B  PART=====
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个学校都非常厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完饭就去练习的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁老师还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗村同学和上条同学也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找找看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个在一起呆着比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁才是主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大一只狗  你是没法养的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我捡到它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有证据的话我是不会交出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙要和我一直生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么还在说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还嫌不够丢人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁才是你真正的主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙刚到我家没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我也不太亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只狗还不太熟悉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  如果是真正主人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该随身带着些散步用的工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太  去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去  可以抵消一点你的丢人程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人都带着粘有同样狗毛的粪便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回到起点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要开始练习了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这两人中至少有一人是为了得到狗而在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  十分感谢能让我们使用这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  反正我们的演奏已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直也承蒙你们关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乐器搬送过来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以练习的时间只有一个小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗村同学和上条同学还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没陷入什么麻烦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买的时候  没有血统证明书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有血统证明书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是别人送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血统证明书是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,项圈上有一把锁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不想让别人把锁取下来的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PIE  SIMATA？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是派的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草莓派的派
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太清楚他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈给它起了一个很复杂的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那SHIMADA是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任主人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(751,629)\fs30}SHIMADA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任主人叫嵨田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他把狗送给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈的名字也叫SHIMADA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给妈妈打个电话确认下比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能和她取得联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道她的手机号码
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了手机  家里的电话记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  果然是在撒谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派是我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不太自然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她看上去不像是为了钱而在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怀疑我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把项圈上的锁打开给你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  这样就能证明我是主人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一听到派就会想起代表圆周率的π
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是3.14
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁都能推测出来的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该有足够的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我把捡到的藏獒拴在公园后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到大厅再回来的空档中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着开锁  去宠物商店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是清理粪便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说可能有点失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不是真正主人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可属于犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡到狗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有立刻去报告保健所或是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你去了大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你是来参加吹奏乐比赛的高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事我可是可以报告给主办方或是学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}您所拨打的电话已关机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为之前在大厅里  所以把电源关掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在老师过来之前  先分部练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  谁才是你真正的主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说句汪或者呜也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点把狗还给我的话  我真的要联系你们学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  看来到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后还是没能找到关键性证据证明谁是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次交易中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是件重要的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又一头栽进麻烦事里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只狗对你来说非常重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  因为它是妈妈买回来十分疼爱的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妈妈的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她送给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她和爸爸分开的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的妈妈还给你什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这只狗一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「爱丽丝镜中奇遇」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯·卡罗尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只狗的名字好像也源于其中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝镜中奇遇中出现的复杂的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs30\pos(640,628)}Humpty  Dumpty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矮胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs30\pos(640,628)}Tweedledum
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叮当兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs30\pos(640,628)}Tweedledee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叮当弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs30\pos(640,628)}Alice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs30\pos(640,628)}Jabberwock
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰伯沃基
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个  杰伯沃基
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来名字是叫阿鲁的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在送给我之前  突然改的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说项圈上的派指的不是名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道你妈妈的联系方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为爸爸说我不能去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.92,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\1c&H7A7A7A&\fs27\fad(180,180)}藏獒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.92,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\1c&H7A7A7A&\fs27\fad(180,180)}挂锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.59,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\1c&H7A7A7A&\fs27\fad(180,180)}杰伯沃基
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.09,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\1c&Hfaffff&\fs27\fad(0,180)}爱丽丝镜中奇遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.09,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\1c&Hfaffff&\fs27\fad(180,180)}突然改名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.43,ONSCREEN I,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\1c&Hfaffff&\fs27\fad(180,180)}无法取得联系的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夏  你带着镜子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  这些文字在镜中映出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ATAMI2314
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住址？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是说不定是犬类名牌的编号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个编号可以在卫生所查到为狗注册时留下的地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里也许是你妈妈住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ATAMI2314
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你妈妈作为财产留下来的藏獒以及给你的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让它再走丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪天我们一起去见妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼的是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷地跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心境发生了什么样的变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明做了那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是无法舍弃指挥棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只有这个才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才紧抓着它不愿放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的交易成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放过你一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待你们的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这是卫生所的电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你脱下尿不湿以后  自己打电话过去咨询吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对爸爸保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他是个好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调解离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来那个孩子是和爸爸一起生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看来分开生活的母亲那边条件更加不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连住址和联系方式都不可以留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这样痛苦的分离啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起对我说  我看你还是快回去和成岛同学道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春太  老师  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:21:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=====NEXT=====
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信二郎的指挥风格变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦率一点吧  小直
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我揭穿你狐狸精的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个自大的孩子
